  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">In <math alttext=\"triangle upper A upper B upper C\"><mo>&#9651;</mo><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></math>,&nbsp;<math alttext=\"angle upper B\"><mo>&#8736;</mo><mi>B</mi></math> is a right angle and the length of&nbsp;<math alttext=\"line segment upper B upper C\"><mover><mrow><mi>B</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math> is <math alttext=\"136\"><mn>136</mn>\n</math> millimeters. If <math alttext=\"cosine upper A equals three fifths\"><mi>cos</mi><mi>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>5</mn></mfrac></math>, what is the length, in millimeters, of <math alttext=\"line segment upper A upper B\"><mover><mrow><mi>A</mi><mi>B</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>?</p>",
